    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_es.00062.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <note type="editorial" resp="#unk" place="top">p 145 | mountain streams | S.D.</note>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Linden Hall,</name>
                    <date when="1881-02-28" rend="right">Feb. 28, '81.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
      
            <p>Having read some 
                of your poems &amp; enjoyed them 
                very much we think our autograph 
                collection is not complete
               without yours, hoping that 
                you will favor us with three 
                we remain,
            </p>
    
            <closer>
                <salute>Yours truly,</salute>
                <signed rend="right">Marie R. Brickenstein,</signed>
                    <signed rend="right">Sallie Potter,</signed>
                   <signed rend="right">E. L. Schessler.</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_es.00061.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
